# 🧩 Issue: Broken Link - "Fundamental Physics for O Level - Teaching Guide" (OUP Pakistan)

## 📖 Overview
While exploring the Physics category on the Oxford University Press (OUP) website, the link for  
**“Fundamental Physics for O Level - Teaching Guide”** does not return a valid result.  

Attempts to access the file through the original URL or Wayback Machine result in errors or restricted access.

---

## 🧠 Problem Description
- The original URL from the OUP Pakistan media page:


https://oup.com.pk/media/teaching-guides/Fundamental%20Biology%20Physics%20Chemistry/Fundamental%20Physics%20for%20O%20Level%20Teaching%20Guide.pdf

no longer returns a valid PDF.

- The global OUP website does not list this Teaching Guide.
- Archived versions on the Wayback Machine may not load the PDF (only the link metadata is stored).
- The OUP Pakistan domain restricts access to certain materials regionally.

---

## ⚠️ Observed Error
When accessing the file, either:
- The **page does not load** (404 or blank), or  
- The **file is region-blocked** (available only within Pakistan).

---

## 💡 Solution

### ✅ 1. Check Alternate Archived Versions
Use the **Wayback Machine** to try older captures:
1. Visit [https://web.archive.org/](https://web.archive.org/)
2. Paste this URL:


https://oup.com.pk/media/teaching-guides/Fundamental%20Biology%20Physics%20Chemistry/Fundamental%20Physics%20for%20O%20Level%20Teaching%20Guide.pdf

3. Check snapshots between **2016–2018**.  
If any capture is available, click to download the file.

---

### 📬 2. Contact OUP Pakistan
Request official access directly from the publisher.

**Email:**


info.pk@oup.com


**Subject:** Request for Teaching Guide - Fundamental Physics for O Level

**Message Template:**


Dear OUP Pakistan Team,

I’m looking for a copy of the "Fundamental Physics for O Level - Teaching Guide."
The link on your media page or archive is not accessible globally.
Kindly share a working link or an official way to obtain this guide.

Regards,
[Your Name]


---

### 🌐 3. Search Alternative Repositories
Try searching for mirrors or reuploads on:
- [academia.edu](https://www.academia.edu)
- [slideshare.net](https://www.slideshare.net)
- [scribd.com](https://www.scribd.com)

Search keywords:


"Fundamental Physics for O Level Teaching Guide OUP Pakistan PDF"


---

### 🧾 4. Use Related Resources
If the specific guide is unavailable:
- Check **OUP Teacher’s Resources** section for equivalent support content.
- Visit the **O Level** section of other OUP regional sites (like OUP India or OUP Global).

---

## 🧩 Conclusion
This issue occurs due to outdated or region-restricted hosting of the Teaching Guide on the OUP Pakistan website.  
The recommended resolution is to:
- Request official access via OUP Pakistan support, or  
- Retrieve an archived copy via the Wayback Machine if available.

